    55→
    56→      <div id="chatMessages" class="bg-slate-800/50 rounded-lg p-4 mb-4 h-64 overflow-y-auto space-y-3">
    57→        <div class="text-gray-400 text-center text-sm">Start a conversation by typing a question below</div>
    58→      </div>
